headline: Dexcom Unveils Season 4 Roster for Game-Changing NIL Program at Signing Day Camp Hosted by Mark Andrews
summary: SAN DIEGO, July 17, 2025--DexCom, Inc. (NASDAQ: DXCM), the global leader in glucose biosensing, announced today the launch of the fourth season of Dexcom U, the company’s one-of-a-kind NIL (Name, Image and Likeness) program exclusively for college athletes with diabetes.
